downloadTitle: Simple Timeline sample diagram for Visio 2010
downloadDescription: This sample diagram, which was generated from the “out-of-the-box” Timeline template and features intelligent shapes, is a companion to The 2010 Visio MVP Sessions, Video 1.
detailsSection: This sample diagram is a companion to The 2010 Visio MVP Sessions (http://visio.microsoft.com/mvpsessions), Video 1 (http://visio.microsoft.com/en-us/Get_Started/How_To/Pages/Get-started-with-the-right-template.aspx), which highlights how to create different diagrams from appropriate “out-of-the-box” templates that each include relevant shape stencils and sometimes include unique, template-specific capabilities. This sample diagram was generated from the Timeline template and features intelligent shapes that can automatically snap to appropriate locations and visually adjust with changes to dates and milestones.
installInstructionSection: Click Download to save the sample diagram to your computer.
